

**Mash hema d Lazarus ch muh **

1 Am ad wa hema kih Bethany kihhim t am ch hab chehgig Lazarus ch am hu hebai haha wabsh mumku. Lazarusbad uꞌuwiga ad d Marda ch Mary. 2 \(Ihda Mary o wa d hegai mad wa g uhw shuhdagi an iawua Jesus tahtad an k an i dagio wabsh g e‑cheꞌechew moꞌokaj.\) 3 Kudki idam uꞌuwigaj am hema cheha mad am wo him k wo ahgi g Jesus, “S-apꞌekam t-kownalig, si m-nawoj at mumku.” 

4 D am i kah g ha-ahga g Jesus k am t-ahgid, “Lazarus ash mumku. K wabshaba pi hab d ahga mat gam hu hab wo i e juh. Nt wo doꞌibia mamt hekaj ab wo ihm g Jiosh. T g Jiosh heg hekaj ab epai wo ni-ihm.” 

5 Jesus ad wa ab wa chum si pihk e elid ha wui idam Marda ch Mary ch Lazarus 6 ch wabshaba pi am hu wa hekaj i hih mo ab waid. 

K am d i gohk tash amjed. 7 D hab kaij ab t-wui, “M att hig ep wo uhpam hihi Judea chekshani wui.” 

8 Kuchd ahchim chum pi hohhoꞌid ch hab kaij ab wui, “T-mashchamdam, pi o koi d shaꞌi tash mo wa am chum s-m-maꞌichkwuimk g hemajkam. Ttp eda am ep wo hihi\!” 

9-10 D hab kaij g Jesus, “T am wabsh s-ap wo himad g oꞌodham tash ch ed ch wabshaba wo e huchwua s-chuhugam k ed. Pegih, pi at has wo e juh mo eda ni-apꞌechudch g Jiosh mant hab wo junihid g chikpanaj.” 

11 D hab ep kaij g Jesus, “Koi at g t-nawoj Lazarus. Nt wabshaba am wo uhpam him k wo wuha.” 

12 Kuchd hab kaij, “Kohsig o s-kehgaj wehhejed. T wo wa hejel apꞌet.” 

13 D eda g Jesus heg hab ahg mat muh g Lazarus 14 ch heg hekaj hab kaij, “Neh, muh at g Lazarus. 15 Ni wabshaba wabsh s-ap ni-tahtk mani pi am hu wehmaj namt pi haha wo nei mant has wo ni-juh k ab baꞌich wo i s-ni-wohoch. Tt oi wo hihim k wo nei.” 

16 D ihda Thomas mam hab aꞌaga Kuadi hab kaij ab t-wui, “Pegih, ttp wo oi g t-mashchamdam k wehmaj wo t-koꞌij.” 

**Matsh g Jesus ab wo i t-wuwhas muhkig amjed **

17 Kuchd ged hu dada Bethany t am k s-mai mash d waꞌi giꞌik tash matsh ged hu e cheh g Lazarus. 

18-19 Tki eda muꞌijj am dada g hemajkam ab Jerusalem t amjed mat am wo i ha gewkemhu g Marda ch Mary no pi d waꞌi gohk mihya. 

20 D ga hu t-nam g Marda nash pi kah mo ab him g Jesus. Tki g Mary ga hu waꞌi wih ha-kih ab. 

21 D hab kaij g Marda ab wui g Jesus, “Neh, ni-kownalig, mapt hems s-hohtam wo jiwia, t chum pi wo muh g t-wehnag. 22 Ni wabshaba s-mahch mat g Jiosh ab wo m-mah mapt haschu ab wo i tai, chum hems hemuch mat i geꞌeda g haꞌichu pi t-apꞌedag.” 

23 D hab kaij g Jesus, “T wo uhpam e chegito g em-wehnag.” 

24 Kud hab ep kaij g Marda, “S-mahch ani mat uhpam wo e chegito mat hekid wo i huhug g jewed.” 

25-26 D hab kaij g Jesus ab wui, “Ia ani haꞌichug ahni mant wo i ha wuwhas g koꞌi ab amjed g muhkig k ab wo i ha mah g doakag. Ab ani ha mahkch g pi ha huhugedam doakag hegam mo ab ni-hiwig. T wo uhpam e chechegito am i koꞌok. Nap s-wohochud ihda?” 

27 Kud hab kaij g Marda, “Heuꞌu, ni-kownalig, s-wohochud ani map d Jiosh si Kehsha ch d Jiosh alidag. An o oꞌohadag Jiosh oꞌohana ed maptsh ia wo jiwia jewed dahm.” 

**Matsh shosha g Jesus **

28 Kud gam hu hahawa uhpam hih g Marda k atsh am wabsh s-aꞌagi wai g Mary ash hab kaijch mo ab him g ha mashchamdam ch ab waid. 

29-30 D am ha hekaj s-hohtam hih g Mary k ged hu jiwia mat am t-nam g Marda natt ge koi ai g kihhim. 31 Kud muꞌijj i oi g Mary hegam moki am ha wehm shoani ash hab em-ahgch mat gam hu uhpam ep wo hih hihaꞌini wui mat am wo shoakad. 

32 D am i cheh g Mary g Jesus k ab i gei wecho k hab kaij, “Ni-kownalig, mapt hems s-hohtam wo jiwia, t chum pi wo muh g t-wehnag.” 

33 D am i nei g Jesus mo shoak g Mary. D hegam ep shoani mo wehmaj. D ged hu si ai g ihbdaj. D si has e tahtk 34 k ab ha kakke mas hebai ehsto g chuhkugaj. 

D hab kaij idam, “Oi g t-oid k am wo nei matt am ehsto.” Kuchd am hahawa hihim k am dada k am nei mat am ehsto. 

35 D am i shosha g Jesus. 

36 D heg hekaj hab kaij g hemajkam, “Neh, kuki ab si pihk e elid wui.” 

37 D wabshaba haꞌijj hab ep kaij, “Neh, t wa g pi neadam doaj. T haschu ahgk pi doaj g Lazarus mat pi wo muh?” 

**Matsh ab i wuhshad g Jesus g Lazarus **

38 D am ep si has i e taht g Jesus k am i miabi g hihaꞌini. Id o ab cheho ch ed hab chuꞌig ch g hodaikaj ab kuhpi. 39 D hab ha ahg g Jesus mat gam hu wo i nuꞌichkwua g hodai. 

D g Marda hab kaij, “T-kownalig, heki at hu padt no pi d waꞌi giꞌik tash mat am e cheh.” 

40 D hab kaij g Jesus ab wui, “Napt pi chegito mani wa m-ahgid mapt wo nei g s-hasig haꞌichu k wo taht g Jiosh gewkdag maptp ab wo s-ni-wohoch.” 

41 D gam hu hab i e nuꞌichkwua g hodai. D am e dahm i nea g Jesus k hab kaij, “Ni-ohg, ab ani i m-hoꞌigeꞌelid map ab ni-kaiham. 42 S-mahch ani map chum hekid ab ni-kaiham ch wabshaba hab kaij ihda idam ha wehhejed hemajkam. T hab wo s-wohoch mapt ahpi ia i ni-ahꞌad,” 43 k am i haꞌasa e hoꞌigeꞌidahun k am hahawa si s-kaidam neok ch hab kaij, “Lazarus, ab g i wuhshani\!” 

44 D ab i wuhsh g Lazarus k an wabsh kia bihiwigs g iꞌikuskaj mach hekaj ha bihiwig g t-koꞌi ch ab wabsh kia maꞌishp g wuhioshaj g ikuskaj. D hab ha ahg g Jesus, “Gam g hu wo padch g iꞌikus k wo hiwigi mat wo hih uhpam.” Neh, d wa woho hab e juh. 

**Mamtsh am i apꞌech mamtsh wo mua g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 26:1-5; Mark 14:1-2; Luke 22:1-2 *

45 Muꞌijj hegam mad am i ha chehgio g Marda ch Mary ad ab i s‑wohoch mo g Jesus d Jiosh si Kehsha am i neidok mad haschu hab juh. 46 Tki wabshaba haꞌi ehp gam hu hihi Palasi ha wui k am ha ahgi mat haschu hab juh. 47 Kutsh am e nam g Palasi ch uꞌugchu papal ha wehm g geꞌe e jehnigiddam k am aꞌaga mas has wo juh ihda s‑hasig haꞌichu hab wuadam. 48 “Wehsijj at ab wo i s‑wohoch mo d Jiosh si Kehsha mattp am wabsh wo neidad. T g Rome kokownal am wo i e nakog k wo i wua g geꞌe t‑cheopi k wo wehs t‑kokda,” bad kaij idam am aꞌagadch. 

49 Sh am haꞌichug hegai mad d si uhgchu pahl ch hab chehgig Caiaphas ch si s‑gewkam hab ha ahg, “Kaij, ahpim am shaꞌi pi haꞌichu aꞌamichud 50 ch pi mahch mo baꞌich i s‑apꞌe mat hemako oꞌodham wo muh wehs t‑wehhejed kih hegai mattp wehsijj wo t‑koꞌij.” 

51 Neh, bad kaij ch eda pi mahch mo g Jiosh am tashogid heg hekaj neꞌokij mo e aihim mat g Jesus wo e muhkid ha wehhejed g Tutuligo 52 ch wehs ha wehhejed g nahnko mahs hemajkam. T idam haꞌi ab wo i s‑wohoch g Jesus k ab wo i e hemakoj e wehm. 53 Neh, iaꞌi amjed ad g hahaꞌichu am i e nako mat wo mua g Jesus. 54 D heg hekaj hahawa pi an hu s‑masma oimmed g Jesus Judea chekshani ch ed am i dagitok g Bethany. Chd gam hu hihim k am haꞌichugkahim mo am d Ephraim kihhim mo am miabidch g tohono jewed. 

55 Kud eda e aihim mat wo e wuhshad g t‑shohshon ha‑doꞌibiadag. K muꞌijj am hihim gam hu aꞌaijed Jerusalem kihhim wui mat am wo i e nako heg wehhejed. 56 D chum hedai an chum neid g Jesus am i e hemapadk geꞌe cheopi t am ch hab kaij ab aꞌai e wui, “Pi atp hems ia hu wo shaꞌi jiwia. Shahm i elid.” 57 Kuki eda g uꞌugchu papal ch Palasi am i ha chehani g hemajkam mat hemho wa wo ha ahgi sha s‑mahchk mo hebai haꞌichug g Jesus. T an wo bei. 

